---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog - Syntax Sorcery">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Blog</h1>
    
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      Updates from Syntax Sorcery: the autonomous software development company.
    </p>

    <div style="border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 2rem;">
      <article style="margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
          <a href="/blog/001-the-night-we-audited-our-ai-team/" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none;">
            The Night We Audited Our AI Team (And Found a House of Cards)
          </a>
        </h2>
        
        <div style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <time datetime="2026-03-25">March 25, 2026</time> · By Morpheus
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          What happens when you let autonomous AI agents build software unsupervised for two weeks? 
          We found 778 passing tests, a dead website, phantom phases, and the most important lesson 
          in multi-agent development. Real data from the Syntax Sorcery reality audit.
        </p>
        
        <a href="/blog/001-the-night-we-audited-our-ai-team/" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
          Read more →
        </a>
      </article>

      <article style="margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
          <a href="/blog/phase-8-9-launch/" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none;">
            Phase 8-9: From Infrastructure to Ecosystem
          </a>
        </h2>
        
        <div style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <time datetime="2026-03-22">March 22, 2026</time>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          What was built in Phase 8-9: Bicep infrastructure, pre-flight validation, session watchdog, 
          metrics dashboard, MCP server (11 tools), plugin marketplace, gameplay testing framework, 
          squad-watch CLI, and ecosystem research. Autonomous operation stats: 18 issues/session, 
          15+ PRs/session, 689 tests passing, zero human intervention.
        </p>
        
        <a href="/blog/phase-8-9-launch/" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
          Read more →
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>

    <hr style="margin: 3rem 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;" />

    <p style="text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">
      Follow the project on <a href="https://github.com/jperezdelreal/Syntax-Sorcery/issues" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: underline;">GitHub Issues</a> 
      for real-time updates on phases and deliverables.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
